# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## 29-11-25 /1

## Changed
- Update readme for new recording functions
- Remove unused code
- Combined the two example tasks into a single folder


## 28-11-25 /1

## Changed
- Update install method for Isaac Sim, Lab and Lerobot

## 31-10-25 /1

# Added
- Policy evaluation in the sim!

# Changed
- Refactor of lerobot_interface to handle sim to real logics inside


## 2025-10-25 /1

### Changed
- Upgrade to support lerobot 0.4.0
- Installation steps are now tricky due to confilicting dependencies

## Added
- List Isaac Sim, Lab and lerobot supported versions


## 2025-10-24 /1

### Added
- Option to cancel recording 
- Asynchronous episode saving

## 2025-10-19 /1

### Added
- multi Camera support
- option to set robot main color

### Changed
- significant refactor to simplify task creation and scalability
- increased realisim by adding depth-of-field and better room asset

### Removed
- removed camera prim from the SO-ARM101-USD asset, it will be spawned during simulation

## 2025-10-13 / 1

### Fixed
- initiating camera using `env.unwrapped`

## 2025-10-09 / 1

### Fixed
- scripts/list_envs.py error `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'omni.appwindow'`
- sim crash when following the quickstart without specifying `repo_id` and `repo_root`
- gracefully exit if dataset folder exists but is not initialized correctly
- spelling

## 2025-10-08 / 1

### Changed
- Better randomization code for the rings and pole

## 2025-10-06 / 1

### Added
- CHANGELOG
- Method to upload dataset to HuggingFace Hub

### Changed
- Recording is now saved as video to reduce storage size and for compatibility
- Camera is created dynamically and using a lens distortion model and parameters that are more similar to the 2MP Camera that is shipped with the robot


### Dependencies
- lerobot[feetech]==0.3.3
- ffmpeg=7.1.1
